              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Calibration: Polarimeter DPOL was primarily designed",
                "and optimized for deuteron polarization measurements.",
                "Therefore the effective analyzing power <Ay> of DPOL",
                "had to be calibrated for protons. It was done at 198",
                "MeV by utilizing the induced polarization Py"
              ]
